{"tid":2515632,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"重建西區警察宿舍縮輪候時間　警方冀吸引年輕人入職","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T06:47:16.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbed94f458691fa910c18f9a13303eb7d5cb714","tid":2515632,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"政府擬重建西區已婚警務人員宿舍，計劃向立法會申請20.2億港元重建3座新警察宿舍，預計可提供540個單位，預計7年後落成。有議員認為，警方對維持本港治安貢獻良多，惟警方的職位空缺多達5,400個，認為可以以宿舍吸引青少年入職。警方回應指，隨着上述宿舍及粉嶺芬園宿舍的落成，預料共可提供逾1,700個單位，相信可藉此提升士氣，吸引更多人加入警隊及挽留人才。"},{"pid":"947eee8605761674a346c407a755e647130fd242","tid":2515632,"uid":26672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:26:55.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦屌你老母，多間狗屋又點，做左都係會折墮，會比人排斥架你班mon po 狗"},{"pid":"dddd005325c1b63f97cb8af8ef238be43542f2a0","tid":2515632,"uid":179967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"有時真係幾羨慕D做狗<br />\n擺低個良心 有錢有屋有人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c93585594227a0d8a0b93aaa41950708e751d3f","tid":2515632,"uid":393145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dddd005325c1b63f97cb8af8ef238be43542f2a0","tid":2515632,"uid":179967,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"有時真係幾羨慕D做狗<br />\n擺低個良心 有錢有屋有人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"擺低自己個良心 有錢有屋有人生<br />\n<br />\n最新警方招人宣傳口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbc33f947862662ea385009f0a0a112b11a17a2","tid":2515632,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:36:46.000Z","msg":"冇得做，又唔係要交番間屋出嚟。"},{"pid":"1582ea0ca6328aeb07516d9297fd861fed70d4e1","tid":2515632,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbc33f947862662ea385009f0a0a112b11a17a2","tid":2515632,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"